name: SP11/SP/2 | Verify user cannot activate Trial period without adding Zip Code
description: Verify user cannot activate Trial period without adding Zip Code
descriptionHtml: Verify user cannot activate Trial period without adding Zip Code

testStage.description: Verify user cannot activate Trial period without adding Zip Code

steps.name: Preconditions: SignUp Trial user without payment
Navigate to Trial user registration page.
Verify user is on Confirm account page.
Retrieve the confirmation link from the user's email.
Fill in the "Full Name On Card" input field
Fill in the "Card Number" input field
Fill in the "Expiration Date" input field
Click on 'Start My 7-Day Free Trial' button.
Verify "Required" sign is popup under the "Billing Zip Code" sign
Verify the empty Zip Code field becomes a pink background color to warn the user

labels.name: titlePath
labels.value: > chromium > registration.spec.js > Negative tests for Trial user registration

labels.name: subSuite
labels.value: Negative tests for Trial user registration
